Package: rwevalidate
Title: Validate Patient Cohorts for Real-World Evidence Studies on OMOP CDM
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Hamid", "Tavakoli", email = "htavakoli@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Validates instantiated patient cohorts on an OMOP Common Data
    Model database for real-world-evidence (RWE) studies. Produces a
    structured HTML and JSON validation report aligned with FDA RWE guidance
    (Relevance and Reliability) and HARPER protocol requirements, covering
    cohort attrition, temporal data density, and (in later versions) concept
    coverage and covariate feasibility.
